OL,3,CHomeless shelter evacuated due to man
OL,4,Con roof ripping off tiles
OL,6,FA homeless shelter has been left with
OL,7,Fsignificant damage after a man climbed
OL,8,Fon the roof to rip off the tiles.
OL,10,FThe council said police were called to
OL,11,Fthe Harbour Place centre in on Tuesday
OL,12,Fnight, 22 May, to reports of a man on
OL,13,Ftop of the building.
OL,15,FStaff and residents had to be
OL,16,Fevacuated and go to the nearby
OL,17,FSalvation Army hostel.
OL,19,FEmergency services attended to resolve
OL,20,Fthe situation and a man was arrested.
