OL,3,CHomeless shelter evacuated due to man
OL,4,Con roof ripping off tiles
OL,6,FOver two thirds of the roof was
OL,7,Fdestroyed and tiles could be seen
OL,8,Fscattered on the street below.
OL,10,FChairman of the Harbour Place
OL,11,FTrustees, Andrew Brown, said the
OL,12,Fdamage was "devastating".
OL,14,FMr Brown estimated the cost could run
OL,15,Finto "many tens of thousands of
OL,16,Fpounds" due to the heavy rainfall
OL,17,Fgetting into the building.
OL,19,FDennis Batty, Director of Harbour
OL,20,FPlace, said he has been overwhelmed by
OL,21,Fthe support of the local community.
