OL,3,CHomeless shelter evacuated due to man
OL,4,Con roof ripping off tiles
OL,6,FMr Batty said as well as support from
OL,7,FNorth East Lincolnshire Council and
OL,8,Fthe Salvation Army, they've been
OL,9,Foffered help from local tradespeople
OL,10,Fto get the building back up and
OL,11,Frunning.
OL,13,FMr Batty said: "It's been a miserable,
OL,14,Fmiserable time for us. But looking at
OL,15,Fit now it does show how well services
OL,16,Fin this area can work together."
