OL,3,CHomeless shelter evacuated due to man
OL,4,Con roof ripping off tiles
OL,6,FMr Batty said that parts of the
OL,7,Fbuilding have been made safe and
OL,8,Fthanks to offers of help, everybody
OL,9,Fwill be housed overnight on Wednesday,
OL,10,F22 May.
OL,12,FHarbour place provides a day centre
OL,13,Fand nine short-stay rooms for people
OL,14,Fwho have been rough sleeping and
OL,15,Fbrought in from the street whilst
OL,16,Flonger term provision is found.
OL,18,FNorth East Lincolnshire Council
OL,19,Fprovide funding for street outreach
OL,20,Fworkers and night staff at the hostel.
