OL,4,Con roof ripping off tiles
OL,6,FCllr Ron Shepherd, from North East
OL,7,FLincolnshire Council said: "Without
OL,8,FHarbour Place, there isn't any
OL,9,Ffacility in the borough to help rough
OL,10,Fsleepers access the support they very
OL,11,Fmuch need, whether short term support
OL,12,Fin the day centre, or support to get
OL,13,Fthem back into appropriate living
OL,14,Faccommodation.
OL,16,F"We will be working with Harbour Place
OL,17,Fin the coming weeks to understand what
OL,18,Fthe longer term impact is whilst the
OL,19,Ffacility is repaired."
